      "oddsUpdateTime": "0001-01-01T01:00:00.000Z",
      "raceComments": "{\"comment\":\"1. EMIRATES AFFAIR is back at the races for the first time since January 24. Worth noting she filled a minor placing when returning from a spell last prep over 1308m at Del Mar. Has found a suitable race. 4. SUNSET HARBOUR ran below expectations last time at Tampa Bay Downs (Dirt), finishing eighth and beaten 26 lengths starting at $9.10. Taking on a better field but she is good enough to turn things around. 3. DEVIL OF PARADIS missed the frame when resuming last start over 1207m at Turfway Park (Synthetic) but wasn't all that far from the winner. Constantino Roman who has scored on her two times retains the mount. Fitter and expected to run well. 6. COASTLINE HOTTIE finished third last start at the first run back from a spell over 1207m at Turfway Park (Synthetic), beaten 1.75 lengths. Meeting a tougher field but on her best form she is right in contention.\",\"runners\":[1,4,3,6],\"exclusive\":false}",
